{"title":"列莫诺夫","authors":["詹永祥"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":2,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"列莫诺夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"詹永祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是一个很坏的天气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列莫诺夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"持枪守卫在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克里姆林宫门口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一动不动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一只鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云朵的阴影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静落满他单薄的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老式军装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的前方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏维埃主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弗拉基米尔·依里奇同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背着手思考问题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他戴着一顶很旧的呢帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"证件忘在贴身的衣兜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列莫诺夫多么优秀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严肃而又认真"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用彬彬有礼的询问"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堵住了克里姆林宫的大门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是从初一的语文课本上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读到这段文字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时列莫诺夫已经退役"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在高加索的一个普通农庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学种土豆和饲养奶牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农闲季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便向少先队员们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲述那段简单而动人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的经历——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列莫诺夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共和国公民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"普通士兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾在执行公务中阻拦过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老资格的布尔什维克"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁同志＊"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}